Nopa ojtli tlen yauiyaya ipan nopa ilhuitl tlen Nearly Headless Nick eltoya tlajko
ika tlauilmej, nojkia, maske nopa tlachiani eliyaya uejka tlen nopa pakilistli: Ni eliyayaj
